This directory contains LaTeX source documents related to the BlackBoard
Selfcal (BBS) System. 

In order to "compile" these sources you need to add the directory
LOFAR/doc/tex/inputs to your TEXINPUTS environment variable, using kpathsea
style. Assuming that you've checked out LOFAR in your home directory, you may
wish to add the following line to your .bashrc file:

export TEXINPUTS=~/LOFAR/doc/tex/inputs//:

